* CONFIGURATION

# A simple example of configuring compiler
variable cc path cc_abs
assign $(path)/$(cc) cc_abs

variable version
assign "0.1a"

menu_item       path_item
link_variable   path

menu_item       cc_item
link_variable   cc
add_description "C Compiler"
add_default     gcc
add_case        gcc
add_case        clang

* REQUIREMENTS

* BUILD

* TEST

* DEPLOY
